patch.description:
This endpoint allows you to Update an existing classified.
## Samples
### Adding or updating the french description text
```json
[
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/data/texts/description/fr",
    "value": "The french description."
  }
]
```
### Removing the main contact's phone number
```json
[
  {
    "op": "remove",
    "path": "/specific/gsl/mainContactPerson/phoneNumber"
  }
]
```
### Adding or updating the showAddress
```json
[
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/data/location/showAddress",
    "value": "false"
  }
]
```
### Adding or updating prices
```json
[
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/data/prices/rent/baseRent/amount",
    "value": "223000"
  },
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/data/prices/brokerageFee/amount",
    "value": "3000"
  }
]
```
